episodes.title: Parents Sentenced to 14 Years For Manslaughter Of Elizabeth Struhs | 10 News First
episodes.description:
She was a little girl who needed insulin.
Instead Elizabeth Struhs' parents let her die a slow and painful death, believing God would heal her.
Matt Johnston joins Ursula with the details.
